ns Coie Political law page] * [http://www.pattonboggs.com/politicallaw/ Patton Boggs Political law page] * [http://www.sandlerreiff.com/practice-areas/ Sandler Reiff & Young] * [http://www.skadden.com/index.cfm?contentID=47&practiceID=43/ Skadden Arps Political law page] * [http://www.tristerross.com/about.html/ Trister, Ross, Schadler & Gold] * [http://www.venable.com/political-law-practices/ Venable LLP political law page] * [http://www.wileyrein.com/practices.cfm?sp=overview&id=4/ Wiley Rein election law and government ethics page] * [http://www.wcsr.com/teams/political-law-practice/ Womble Carlyle Political law page] * [https://its.law.nyu.edu/facultyprofiles/profile.cfm?section=bio&personID=20200/ Rick Pildes biography] * [http://its.law.nyu.edu/facultyprofiles/profile.cfm?personID=23845/ Samuel Issacharoff biography] * [http://www.Electionlawblog.org/ Election law blog] * [http://www.PoliticalActivityLaw.com/ Political activity law blog]
